As she finishes the rotation, she begins to walk confidently forward. The camera simultaneously swivels in a smooth orbital arc around her, moving from her face to behind her shoulder. She walks toward a sheer cliff edge as the camera follows her.

The camera movement reveals a breathtaking, expansive vista of foggy mountains and ancient crumbling architecture in the distance. The lighting is soft and cold, capturing the detailed texture of her leather gloves and the falling snow.
